Package: Seqtometry
Title: Signature scoring for single cell analysis
Version: 0.1.0
URL: https://github.com/HawigerLab/Seqtometry
Authors@R: c( 
    person("Robert", "Kousnetsov", email = "robert.kousnetsov@health.slu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Daniel", "Hawiger", email = "daniel.hawiger@health.slu.edu", role = c("cph")))
Description: 
    This package provides the Seqtometry scoring algorithm for the generation of single cell 
    gene set (signature) enrichment scores for scRNA-seq or scATAC-seq data.
